'''Ruiko Saten''' is a character in the comic ''[[A Certain Scientific Railgun]]'' and its derivative works. She also appears in ''[[A Certain Magical Index|A Certain Magical Index: The Movie – The Miracle of Endymion]]''. 
==Basic Information==
She is a one grader in [[Sakugawa Middle School]]. With long hair decorated with white flowers. Though looks like to be an optimistic and simple person, she is very sensitive to feelings of people around. 
{{spoiler|She is obsessive with [[Kazari Uiharu]]'s dress.}}
